Interview questions: 
 1. relation between start and run
 -->when start() method is called, a new thread is created and run() method is implemented.
 -->when run() method is called it directly go and implement run() method without creating a thread.
 
 2. how to use runnable thread 
 by overriding run method inside it and passing it to a thread class.
 
 3. can i invoke run method explicitly 
  yes we can invoke run method explicitly but it is not recommended
  
 4. What are the constructors of Thread class?
  Thread(){
  }
  Thread(Runnable object){
  }